   "body" : "This fixes bugs where we end up banning peers running different consensus rules (including old nodes following a softfork). Since we rely on having peers enforcing the same rules as us, it also enforces that outbound non-feeler connections must have and maintain the same tip block; if they diverge from us, we disconnect them (and find a replacement).",
